  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  All healthy women older than 70 years with sufficient knowledge of German can
             participate.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Chronic mental disorders

          -  Chronic neurological, cardiological, pulmonary or renal diseases.

          -  Severe osteoarthritis

          -  Disorders which can be aggravated by exercise (arterial hypertension, coronary heart
             disease, COLD).

          -  Cancer in current therapy

          -  Treatment with glucocorticoids or cytostatic drugs.

          -  Patients who received an organ transplantation

          -  Exercise-induced osteoarticular pain
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
